form diving competition\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spendolini-Sirieix had a poor second dive in Tuesday's final and then was never really in contention in her quest for asecond medal after bronze in the synchro competitioneventually finishing in sixth place.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"a poor second dive\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"her quest\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"asecond medal\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 569}, {\"ngram\": \"the synchro\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"sixth place\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 19-year-old was tearful in the aftermath saying she felt lucky to be alive and competing in Paris.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 734, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999849360394, \"rank\": 1.5063856204474077e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the aftermath\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told the BBC: \\\"Obviously it wasn't the result that I wanted.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9162843177285891, \"rank\": 0.06127894726631377, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not even upset with the competition.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": 