ho I am.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one medal\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was just God's way of saying there is more to do and I just give God all the glory.\\\"\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"God's way\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"all the glory\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 2464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1646, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9998625115047473, \"rank\": 7.938868163462788e-05, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9998625115047473, \"rank\": 7.938868163462788e-05, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"],